<div class="container-lg">
	<div class="main-layout">
		<aside class="emba-aside">
			<%= render :partial => "/partials/accordian_nav" %>
		</aside>
		<main class="emba-main">
		    <h2 class="main-title">Case Classroom</h2>
			
			<div class="classroom-wrapper">
				<div class="room-item">
				    <div class="room-hd">
					    <span class="num">01</span>
						<span class="name">E.Sun Hall</span>
					</div>
					<div class="room-bd">
					    <div class="bd-left">
							<!-- 後台請註明上傳圖片 1200x750 或等比(4:3)) -->
                            <div id="carouselRoomControls_01" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                                <div class="carousel-inner">
                                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                                        <img src="../assets/fake/room_01.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="carousel-item">
                                        <img src="../assets/fake/room_02.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." />
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="carousel-item">
                                        <img src="../assets/fake/room_03.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselRoomControls_01" data-bs-slide="prev">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                                </button>
                                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselRoomControls_01" data-bs-slide="next">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
						</div>
						<div class="bd-right">
						    <p>As NTU College of Management’s first seminar room, “E.Sun Hall” was officially opened in 2006. Donated by E.Sun Bank, E. Sun Hall is the first case classroom in the nation. Located on the 3rd floor of the NTU College of Management building I, the classroom has its design emphasized on the audio-visual requirement of a globe theater like classroom. By offering teachers and learners a space to sufficiently interact with each another, it has created a “learner-centered” learning environment to help participants establishing logic of making a comprehensive decision.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
