                                    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                                </button>
                                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselRoomControls_02" data-bs-slide="next">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
						</div>
						<div class="bd-right">
						    <p>NTU College of Management’s second case classroom “Kindom Hall” was officially launched in 2007. Donated by the Chairman of Kindom Construction, Yu-Shan Ma, this brand new case classroom on the 2nd floor of NTU College of Management building I has copied U.S. Harvard Business School’s pattern as a learner-centered platform adopted case teaching methods. </p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="room-item">
				    <div class="room-hd">
					    <span class="num">03</span>
						<span class="name">Jhong Guang Hall</span>
					</div>
					<div class="room-bd">
